In this edition of Trend is the Mindkiller, Jack and Miles discuss Rolling Stone's Jan. 6 'expose', the World Series, Alec Baldwin having some 'splaining to do, thoughts on 'Dune', Hertz ordering 100k Teslas, and the John Mulaney/Olivia Munn situation.
